OL,7,FIn contrast, a smaller proportion of
OL,8,Folder workers said they were taking
OL,9,Ftime off for stress ` some 14% of 45
OL,10,Fto 54-year-olds, down from 18% the
OL,11,Fprevious year, and 10% of workers aged
OL,12,F55 and above, down from 15%.
