OL,3,CYounger workers more likely to suffer
OL,4,Cburnout as generation gap grows `
OL,5,Csurvey
OL,7,FIn what the charity described as a
OL,8,F"warning sign of a breakdown in trust
OL,9,Fbetween employers and younger
OL,10,Fworkers", its findings showed only a
OL,11,Flittle over half (56%) of 18 to 24-
OL,12,Fyear-olds said they would feel
OL,13,Fcomfortable opening up to a line
OL,14,Fmanager about the pressure and stress
OL,15,Fthey felt.
OL,17,FThis was a sharp drop from 75% of this
OL,18,Fage group in the previous report.
