OL,3,CYounger workers more likely to suffer
OL,4,Cburnout as generation gap grows `
OL,5,Csurvey
OL,7,FWhen it comes to switching off from
OL,8,Fwork, only a third (33%) of 18 to 24-
OL,9,Fyear-olds said they could when they
OL,10,Fneeded to, compared with 46% of those
OL,11,Faged 55 and above.
OL,13,FBrian Dow, the charity's chief
OL,14,Fexecutive, said their findings show
OL,15,Fthat "many organisations still offer
OL,16,F20th-century mental health support for
OL,17,Fa 21st-century workforce".
