OL,4,Cburnout as generation gap grows `
OL,5,Csurvey
OL,7,FHe said: "Our survey clearly reveals
OL,8,Fit is young people most at risk of
OL,9,Fhigh stress in the workplace, but
OL,10,Fraises doubts around whether they feel
OL,11,Fable to open up to their line manager
OL,12,Fand explore reasonable adjustments
OL,13,Fthat could help prevent burnout.
OL,15,F"As the gap between generations
OL,16,Fwidens, there's a need to rebuild
OL,17,Fbridges and open up conversations on
OL,18,Fchanging attitudes and expectations
OL,19,Faround work.
